# GitHub Sync

Repository: https://github.com/tg181185klo-png/finance

After completing any code change in this project:
1. Run `git add -A`
2. Commit with a clear message describing what changed
3. Run `git push origin main`

Do not commit: `.env.local`, `node_modules`, `.next`, `data/store.json` (local business data).

Environment variables for production are set in Vercel dashboard.
